data.title: Geography 9th
data.meta_description:
Geography 9th - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The document discusses India's size, location, and physical features. It provides multiple choice questions and
answers about key facts like India's easternmost longitude, neighboring countries, and physiographic divisions. It
also describes in paragraphs how the Himalayas were formed due to tectonic plate movement, and provides an
account of the Northern Plains of India and how they were formed by sediment deposition from rivers.
